      <p class="text-lg">
        <strong>These aren't direct competitors - they solve different problems.</strong> Hostinger is budget hosting with a basic website builder thrown in. Mixo is an AI website builder with hosting as an add-on. <span class="font-bold">Choose Hostinger (7/10) if you want the cheapest possible solution and don't care about having the best design. Choose Mixo (8/10) if you want AI-generated beautiful website and don't mind paying separately for hosting. For most people, Mixo's design quality is worth the extra cost. Hostinger is only for ultra-budget-conscious users.</span>
